name: R4B-AuditEvent-R5-AuditEvent
title: Concept map to convert a FHIR R4B AuditEvent into FHIR R5

element.display: Event record kept for security purposes

target.comment: R4B `AuditEvent` maps as Equivalent to R5 `AuditEvent`

element.display: Type of action performed during the event

target.display: Type of action performed during the event
target.comment: R4B `AuditEvent.action` maps as Equivalent to R5 `AuditEvent.action` - action has compatible required binding for code type: http://hl7.org/fhir/ValueSet/audit-event-action|4.3.0 and http://hl7.org/fhir/ValueSet/audit-event-action|5.0.0 (Equivalent)
R4B `AuditEvent.agent` maps as Equivalent to R5 `AuditEvent.agent`
R4B `AuditEvent.agent.extension` maps as RelatedTo to R5 `AuditEvent.agent.extension` - extension has change due to type change: R4B `extension` `Extension` maps as RelatedTo for R5 `extension`
R4B `AuditEvent.agent.id` maps as Equivalent to R5 `AuditEvent.agent.id`

target.display: The agent location when the event occurred
target.comment: R4B `AuditEvent.agent.location` maps as Equivalent to R5 `AuditEvent.agent.location`

target.comment: R4B `AuditEvent.agent.modifierExtension` maps as RelatedTo to R5 `AuditEvent.agent.modifierExtension` - modifierExtension has change due to type change: R4B `modifierExtension` `Extension` maps as RelatedTo for R5 `modifierExtension`

R4B `AuditEvent.contained` maps as Equivalent to R5 `AuditEvent.contained`
